name: %block
valid contents: p, ol, ul, h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6, pre, dl, div, center, noscript,noframes, blockquote, form, isindex, hr, table, fieldset, address

name: %fontstyle
valid contents: tt, i, b, u, s, strike, big, small

name: %phrase
valid contents: em, strong, dfn, code, samp,kbd, var, cite, abbr, acronym

name: %special
valid contents: a, img, applet, object, font, basefont, br, script, map, q, sub, sup, span, bdo, iframe

name: table
valid contents: caption, col, colgroup, thead, tfoot, tbody
